Avaya BCMS Splunk App provides Splunk real time dashboards for Avaya Aura CM platform. The Avaya BCMS Splunk App is part of a solution call bcmsSVR which integrates with Avaya CM directly and provides real time and historical reports for call center users. For detail information of bcmsSVR, please visit https://blog.upinget.com/2014/09/27/bcmssvr/

The Avaya BCMS Splunk App is created by UPINGET Technologies. 
Please contact service@upinget.com for technical support.  
